1082→// Frame push/pop is now active: run() wraps each evaluation in a child region.
1083→// Temporary Values (ints, cons cells, intermediate strings) die with the child
1084→// region. Long-lived values are promoted to root_region by existing infrastructure:
1085→// - jit_make_closure_from_expr: allocates closures in root_region, deep-copies env
1086→// - jit_eval_define: copies defined values to root_region via copy_to_parent
1087→// - jit_eval_let_rec: promotes rec_env to root_region when in child frame
1088→// - alloc_expr/alloc_pattern: always use root_region (AST nodes survive)
